    "updated_at": "2023-11-12T19:08:03Z",
    "body": "At this time, the existing transient integrations don't do much integration with the shell, mostly only providing a method to set up one's own transient prompt.\r\nYou can style the `TRANSIENT_PROMPT` as you wish with something like `starship module character` or `starship prompt --profile=transient` (this requires a `profile.transient` top-level format string). Nevertheless, the nushell feature might be worth mentioning in our docs.",
